  # Claude Projects: Complete Guide + Setup Tutorial (2025)
  
  [![Melissa Onwuka](https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fill:32:32/1*-sLLn2JruOfIaJf20kHpYg@2x.jpeg)](https://melissaonwuka.medium.com/?source=post_page---byline--3b9a60033b59---------------------------------------)
  
  [Melissa Onwuka](https://melissaonwuka.medium.com/?source=post_page---byline--3b9a60033b59---------------------------------------)
  
  Follow
  
  8 min read
  
  ·
  
  Dec 24, 2025
  
