  [Listen](https://medium.com/m/signin?actionUrl=https%3A%2F%2Fmedium.com%2Fplans%3Fdimension%3Dpost_audio_button%26postId%3D3b9a60033b59&operation=register&redirect=https%3A%2F%2Fmelissaonwuka.medium.com%2Fclaude-projects-complete-guide-setup-tutorial-2025-3b9a60033b59&source=---header_actions--3b9a60033b59---------------------post_audio_button------------------)
  
