  # Claude's new AI superpowers 🚀
  
  ### Check out a surprisingly useful new way to use AI
  
  [![Jeremy Caplan's avatar](https://substackcdn.com/image/fetch/$s_!wnwT!,w_36,h_36,c_fill,f_auto,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep/https%3A%2F%2Fbucketeer-e05bbc84-baa3-437e-9518-adb32be77984.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2F71a60be2-fb37-4515-94bc-82e21a1b3269_339x433.jpeg)](https://substack.com/@wondertools)
  
